{"type":"message","id":"cef99938","parentId":"b4e6bbdf","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:17:33.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"QA for Company Intel Dashboard V3 is complete.\n\nFound critical issues with missing style.css file, mismatched filenames in index.html referencing styles.css and app.js instead of style.css and script.js, and element ID mismatches between index.html and script.js breaking filtering UI. Also found inconsistencies in data field names between companies.v3.json and script.js that break logic.\n\nCreated a QA report summarizing:\n- Critical issues (missing style.css, broken references, ID and field mismatches)\n- Medium issues (missing optional fields for tasks, pros, cons)\n- Quick wins with minimal safe fixes to get the dashboard working\n- Fail recommendation currently, pass after fixes\n\nReport saved to OpenClawMissionControl/dashboard/company-intel-v3/QA_REPORT_KELLY.md for morning handoff.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02c22ab212ee4de40069af7129e3c0819f931c5784a3bee6a5\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":12391,"output":162,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12553,"cost":{"input":0.0049564000000000006,"output":0.0002592,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005215600000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773105447246}}
